title: Olympian Andy Butchart - 6th 2016 Olympic Games, 8th 2017 World Championships
description:
Todays podcast rants with GBs Andy Butchart, covers a few things:

*Self Belief - Going all in
*Tips from Mo Farah - Butchart being close to Mo
*Comeback from broken Navicular - Missing all of 2018 essentially
*Goals for 2019 -
And much more, lots to gain from listening to this one.
